Kostek Wojciechowski (43)
Since childhood was fascinated by computers.
Worked as print designer, pre-press engineer, web designer, UX/UI designer, usabilist, front-end developer...
Now he is an aspiring game developer/designer.
In his free time he works as a husband and proud father of 5.5 years old son.
He likes to cook and practices Taijiquan.
